#: src/app/[locale]/customers/netzero/page.tsx
msgid "What convinced Olivier was the flexibility of the platform and where it was headed. Even when initial needs were basic record-keeping, he still needed a custom data model with granular permissions to manage the wide range of NetZero activities. He also needed a system that could adapt quickly to a fast-iteration company."
